content.text:
Let me analyze and solve this building block challenge:

Main Target Image Analysis:
- Total Blocks: 7 blocks
- Colors: Red (4 blocks), Green (1 block), Blue (1 block), Yellow (1 block), Orange (1 block top triangular block)
- Layers: 3-4 layers high
- Unique Structure: Features arch-like red blocks at bottom and top, with other blocks stacked in between

Required Blocks from Dictionary:
1. Red arch block (index 1): Bottom base (2 pieces)
2. Red arch block (index 2): Top layer supporting orange triangular block
3. Green cube (index 8)
4. Blue cube (index 7)
5. Yellow rectangular block (index 10)
6. Orange triangular block (index 15)

Assembly Instructions:
{
    Step1: Move block with index 1 (red arch)
    Step2: Move block with index 1 (second red arch)
    Step3: Move block with index 10 (yellow rectangular block)
    Step4: Move block with index 7 (blue cube)
    Step5: Move block with index 8 (green cube)
    Step6: Move block with index 2 (red arch on top)
    Step7: Move block with index 15 (orange triangular block)
}
